"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-4-10-olympics-indias-zareen-ready-to-step-out-of-mary-koms-shadow-says-coach\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The current IBA women's world boxing champion will go for gold at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 85, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9758904878197221, \"rank\": 0.024021894956547815, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Two-time world boxing champion Nikhat Zareen is ready to step out of fellow Indian MC Mary Kom's shadow with a medal at the Paris Olympics, coach Blas Iglesias Fernandez has said.\", \"from\": 87, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7146262475198844, \"rank\": 0.334929490889726, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Kom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MC Mary Kom\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Kom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Kom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Six-time world champion MC Mary Kom has been the face of women's boxing in India and her illustrious career inspired a Bollywood biopic in 2014.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Kom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MC Mary Kom\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http: